<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM12.5">
<l>ārkkumeṉ ṉōyi taṟiyalākā tammaṉai mīrtuḻa tippaṭātē</l>
<l>kārkkaṭal vaṇṇaṉeṉ pāṉoruvaṉ kaikaṇṭa yōkan taṭavattīrum</l>
<l>nīrkkarai niṉṟa kaṭampaiyēṟik kāḷiya ṉucciyil naṭṭampāyntu</l>
<l>pōrkkaḷa māka niruttañceyta poykaik karaikkeṉṉai yuyttiṭumiṉ.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O mothers! No one can know this disease of mine. Without feeling sorrow,</l>
<l>Send me to the banks of the pond where [He] danced so that [it] became a battlefield,</l>
<l rend="indent">Climbing upon the Cadamba tree that stood by the banks of the waterbody</l>
<l rend="indent">And leaping as a dance on the crown of Kāliya’s head!</l>
<l>[This disease] will end as a man called the black ocean-hued [Lord] strokes [me].</l>
<l rend="indent">This is an efficient cure!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
